=====================================================================
4. DNS QUERY FLOW
=====================================================================


                DNS REQUEST FLOW

    ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
    │ 192.168.1.5:53000                  │
    │             ↓                      │
    │      192.168.1.1:53                │
    └─────────────────────────────────────┘


Example DNS request:

192.168.1.5:53000
-> 192.168.1.1:53


Yahan:

192.168.1.5
= laptop private IP

53000
= temporary client port assigned by OS
(ephemeral port)

53
= DNS server port


NOTE:
Client side par ports usually temporary hote hain.
Server side par ports mostly fixed/well-known hote hain.


Examples:

53  -> DNS
80  -> HTTP
443 -> HTTPS


=====================================================================
5. ROUTER DOES PAT (Port Address Translation)
=====================================================================

People casually "NAT" bol dete hain.

But technically:

NAT
= only IP translation

PAT
= IP + Port translation


Home routers usually PAT use karte hain because:
multiple devices same public IP share karte hain.


                    BEFORE PAT

    192.168.1.5:53000
            │
            ▼
      8.8.8.8:53


                     AFTER PAT

    49.205.10.20:61000
            │
            ▼
       8.8.8.8:53


Yahan router:
- private IP replace karta hai apne public IP se
- source port bhi remap karta hai


=====================================================================
WHY PORT TRANSLATION IS ALSO NEEDED?
=====================================================================

IMPORTANT.

Suppose:

Laptop:
192.168.1.5:4321

Phone:
192.168.1.7:4321


Dono devices same source port use kar sakte hain internally.


Agar router sirf IP translate kare aur port same rakhe:

❌ INVALID:

49.205.10.20:4321
49.205.10.20:4321


To ambiguity ho jayegi.

Router ko pata nahi chalega:
response laptop ke liye tha ya phone ke liye.


Isliye router unique public-side ports assign karta hai:


✔ VALID:

Laptop:
49.205.10.20:3921

Phone:
49.205.10.20:3922


Isi wajah se PAT powerful hai.


