CASE 2
DNS SERVER = 8.8.8.8
---------------------------------------------------------------------


Suppose DHCP ne DNS server diya hota:

    8.8.8.8  (Google DNS)


Ab laptop subnet check karta aur conclude karta:

    "8.8.8.8 mere local network me nahi hai."


Ab is case me: gateway use hoga.


                    FLOW

    Laptop
        │
        ▼
    Gateway / Router
        │
        ▼
    Google DNS
      8.8.8.8


Matlab:

    Subnet batata hai:
        destination local hai ya nahi.

    Aur agar destination local nahi hai,
    to packet gateway/router ko bheja jata hai.


